Changelog 5-24-2024

Watchtower 2.1.1 REBUILD

Completely rebuilt the stack on its own VLAN

Hypervisors now on dedicated VLAN

Two nodes removed for ARP table scraping and no longer in cluster

Fix all things associated with a rebuild

Multi-master design

L2, L3, and L4 routing all happen locally

Fixed DNS to point to new stack

Updated endpoint telemetry collection to send data to the new stack

Recreated backup infrastructure

Recreated Watchtower Forensic Datastore

Significant performance and usability improvements

Custom kernel parameters for KVM access and hugepages

Database performance improvement

Fixed all symbolic links pointing to old infrastructure with adaptive links to reduce future maintenance requirements

GUI improvements

Result of changes:

Recreated stack
